-t "Members"

%p
  SD Ruby is an awesome group of designers, developers, and all-around cool people.
  At present, we have
  = User.count
  users, created over 34 open-source projects, and given 64 talks about Ruby and related topics.

%table#members
  - @users.each do |user|
    %tr.member
      %td= link_to(image_tag(user.avatar.url(:small), :size => "48x48"), user)
      %td= link_to user.full_name, user
      - if user.neighborhood?
        %td= user.neighborhood
      - else
        %td ...
      - if user.github_projects?
        %td= pluralize(YAML::load(user.github_projects || 0).size, 'project')
      - else
        %td ...
      
%br/
